collections::linked_list::LinkedList::<T.doc:
Adds an element to the back of the list.

This operation should compute in *O*(1) time.

# Examples

```
use std::collections::LinkedList;

let mut d = LinkedList::new();
d.push_back(1);
d.push_back(3);
assert_eq!(3, *d.back().unwrap());
```

